# CODEOWNERS
# See https://docs.github.com/en/repositories/managing-your-repositorys-settings-and-features/customizing-your-repository/about-code-owners
#
# Replace @your-org/platform-maintainers with your actual GitHub team or user handles.

# Global default
*                           @your-org/platform-maintainers

# Infrastructure changes require infrastructure team review
infrastructure/             @your-org/infrastructure-team
infrastructure/terraform/   @your-org/infrastructure-team
infrastructure/ansible/     @your-org/infrastructure-team

# Security policies and Vault/RBAC changes require security team review
security/                   @your-org/security-team
security/vault/             @your-org/security-team
security/rbac/              @your-org/security-team
.github/workflows/          @your-org/security-team @your-org/platform-maintainers

# GitOps / Helm chart changes require platform and SRE review
gitops/                     @your-org/sre-team @your-org/platform-maintainers
gitops/helm-charts/         @your-org/sre-team @your-org/platform-maintainers
gitops/argocd/              @your-org/sre-team @your-org/platform-maintainers

# CI/CD configuration changes
Jenkinsfile                 @your-org/platform-maintainers
.github/workflows/          @your-org/platform-maintainers
